# Local test bridge daemon.
#
# Start this with a tor binary, then run mixtor-server in front of it:
# mixtor-server --listen 127.0.0.1:9001 --upstream 127.0.0.1:9002

DataDirectory ./target/local-tor-bridge-data
SocksPort 0
BridgeRelay 1
ORPort 127.0.0.1:9002
AssumeReachable 1
PublishServerDescriptor 0
ExitRelay 0
Nickname mixtorlocal
ContactInfo local-test
Log notice stdout
